# COPY INTO vs. Auto Loader

Both load files into Delta, both idempotent — pick by *operational shape*.

| | `COPY INTO` | Auto Loader |
|---|---|---|
| API | Pure SQL | Structured Streaming |
| Idempotency | Delta load history | Streaming checkpoint |
| Best for | Daily batch, few files | Continuous / high-volume |
| Schema evolution | Manual per run | Built-in |
| Throughput | Hundreds–thousands | Millions+ (notification) |
| Latency | Cron cadence | Down to seconds |

## The most common exam pattern

- *Continuous arrival, schema may evolve* → **Auto Loader**
- *One daily batch, simple SQL* → **`COPY INTO`**
